  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/244364.htm", 
  "description": "<p>据《日经新闻》报道，虽然现在已是智能手机游戏的天下，但也许你依旧难忘当年任天堂红白机的迷人风采。<strong>红白机上市即将迎来30周年纪念，这款游戏机 的幕后推手上村雅之（Uemura Masayuki）目前任教于日本立命馆大学，致力将自己的心得传承给年轻学子。一起来听听他和红白机的故事，以及他对有志开发游戏者的忠告。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e8aef45/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244364.htm&amp;t=%E4%BB%BB%E5%A4%A9%E5%A0%82%E5%85%83%E8%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%80%85%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E7%8E%A9%E8%80%8D%E6%89%8D%E6%9C%89%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244364.htm&amp;t=%E4%BB%BB%E5%A4%A9%E5%A0%82%E5%85%83%E8%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%80%85%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E7%8E%A9%E8%80%8D%E6%89%8D%E6%9C%89%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244364.htm&amp;t=%E4%BB%BB%E5%A4%A9%E5%A0%82%E5%85%83%E8%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%80%85%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E7%8E%A9%E8%80%8D%E6%89%8D%E6%9C%89%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244364.htm&amp;t=%E4%BB%BB%E5%A4%A9%E5%A0%82%E5%85%83%E8%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%80%85%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E7%8E%A9%E8%80%8D%E6%89%8D%E6%9C%89%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/goog