  "description": "<p><strong>微软周四公布了内部重组方案，将当前的8个产品部门整合为4个新部门，以实现“一个微软、一个战略”的目标。</strong>微软CEO史蒂夫•鲍尔默(Steve Ballmer)随后发表了一份备忘录，重点谈到了本次公司重组。他表示，这次重组具有非常重要的意义，它能够让微软以更快速、更高效和更大的能量进行创新，从而更好的适应这个高速发展的社会。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e8aef44/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244363.htm&amp;t=%E9%B2%8D%E5%B0%94%E9%BB%98%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98%E5%BD%95%E8%B0%88%E9%87%8D%E7%BB%84%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF+%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%88%98%E7%95%A5\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244363.htm&amp;t=%E9%B2%8D%E5%B0%94%E9%BB%98%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98%E5%BD%95%E8%B0%88%E9%87%8D%E7%BB%84%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF+%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%88%98%E7%95%A5\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244363.htm&amp;t=%E9%B2%8D%E5%B0%94%E9%BB%98%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98%E5%BD%95%E8%B0%88%E9%87%8D%E7%BB%84%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF+%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%88%98%E7%95%A5\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244363.htm&amp;t=%E9%B2%8D%E5%B0%94%E9%BB%98%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98%E5%BD%95%E8%B0%88%E9%87%8D%E7%BB%84%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF+%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%88%98%E7%95%A5\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.c